                                                                  Our privacy policy

This policy will help you understand the following:

1. Our commitment

2. How do we collect and use your user information

3. How do we protect your user information

4. How to contact us

1. Our commitment:

We are well aware of the importance of user information to you and will do our best to protect the security and reliability of your user information. We are committed to maintaining your trust in US and abide by the following principles to protect your user information: the principle of consistent rights and responsibilities, the principle of clear purpose, the principle of choice and consent, the principle of minimum adequacy, the principle of ensuring security, the principle of subject participation, the principle of openness and transparency, etc. At the same time, we promise that we will take corresponding security measures to protect your user information according to the mature security standards in the industry.

2. Use of user information

This is an excellent computer screen recording software. When you use our products, please allow us to use your computer desktop screenshot and your microphone sound to record video

3. How do we protect your user information

We promise that your user information will only be saved locally on your computer for your personal use. We will not collect any of your personal user information

4. Contact us

If you have any suggestions, you can leave a message to us through windows store, and we will follow up and reply in time
